</figureCitation>
C. Distance between eyes 
<quantity id="BC6991D451323C3BE5A9FC8C4E296C6E" box="[981,1091,799,823]" metricMagnitude="-4" metricUnit="m" metricValue="3.3" pageId="30" pageNumber="181" unit="mm" value="0.33">0.33 mm</quantity>
. Chaetotaxy of mentum and submentum 
<figureCitation id="E3AA20B451323C3BE75DFCD14B196C03" box="[289,371,834,859]" captionStart="FIGURE 21. A" captionStartId="31.[151,250,1826,1848]" captionTargetBox="[183,1416,339,1758]" captionTargetId="figure@31.[153,1438,305,1801]" captionTargetPageId="31" captionText="FIGURE 21. A. lauta. A, habitus; B, side of pronotum viewed at 45 ˚; C, antennomeres 3 – 11; D, aedeagus; E, ventrite six; F, ventrite seven; G, mesoventral collar x 385; H metaventral posterior margin and metacoxal plates; I, mentum and submentum showing chaetotaxy." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/249576/files/figure.png" pageId="30" pageNumber="181">
