Fig. 
<number id="CD592E1651323C3BE5DDFC1849D66CFB" box="[929,956,907,931]" pageId="30" pageNumber="181" value="21.0">21</number>
</figureCitation>
G. Posterior margin of metasternum and metacoxal plates 
<figureCitation id="E3AA20B451323C3BE725FC3D4BC06C9F" box="[345,426,942,967]" captionStart="FIGURE 21. A" captionStartId="31.[151,250,1826,1848]" captionTargetBox="[183,1416,339,1758]" captionTargetId="figure@31.[153,1438,305,1801]" captionTargetPageId="31" captionText="FIGURE 21. A. lauta. A, habitus; B, side of pronotum viewed at 45 ˚; C, antennomeres 3 – 11; D, aedeagus; E, ventrite six; F, ventrite seven; G, mesoventral collar x 385; H metaventral posterior margin and metacoxal plates; I, mentum and submentum showing chaetotaxy." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/249576/files/figure.png" pageId="30" pageNumber="181">
